def test_report_exception_runs_task(app: Sanic):
    c = count()

    async def task_1():
        next(c)

    async def task_2(app):
        next(c)

    @app.report_exception
    async def catch_any_exception(app: Sanic, exception: Exception):
        next(c)

    @app.route("/")
    async def handler(request):
        app.add_task(task_1)
        app.add_task(task_1())
        app.add_task(task_2)
        app.add_task(task_2(app))
        return empty()

    app.test_client.get("/")

    assert next(c) == 4
